import React from "react";
import { Code, Database, BookOpen } from 'react-feather'
import {
  Card,
  Box,
  Button,
  Image,
  Stack,
  Set,
  Heading,
  Container,
  Columns,
  Text,
  Paragraph,
  Badge,
} from "bumbag";

const Skills = () => (
  <Container padding="2rem 1rem">
    <Heading use="h4" marginBottom="major-4">
      Skills
    </Heading>

    <Set spacing='major-2'>
      {/* <Box> */}
        <Card altitude="200" textAlign='left' padding='2rem'>
          <Code color='#5863D8'/>
          <Heading use='h4' fontWeight='semibold' paddingTop='2rem' paddingBottom='1.5rem'>Languages</Heading>
        <Set orientation='vertical' spacing="major-2">
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>Java</Paragraph> 
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>JavaScript</Paragraph> 
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>C++</Paragraph> 
          </Set>
        </Card>
      {/* </Box> */}

      {/* <Box> */}
      <Card altitude="200" textAlign='left' padding='2rem'>
          <Database color='#5863D8'/>
          <Heading use='h4' fontWeight='semibold' paddingTop='2rem' paddingBottom='1.5rem'>Database</Heading>
        <Set orientation='vertical' spacing="major-2">
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>SQL Server</Paragraph> 
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>MySQL</Paragraph> 
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>MongoDB</Paragraph> 
          </Set>
        </Card>
      {/* </Box> */}

      {/* <Box> */}
      <Card altitude="200" textAlign='left' padding='2rem'>
          <BookOpen color='#5863D8'/>
          <Heading use='h4' fontWeight='semibold' paddingTop='2rem' paddingBottom='1.5rem'>Libraries</Heading>
        <Set orientation='vertical' spacing="major-2">
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>React.js</Paragraph> 
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>Node.js</Paragraph> 
          <Paragraph color='secondary'>Spring.java</Paragraph> 
          </Set>
        </Card>
      {/* </Box> */}
    </Set>
  </Container>
);

export default Skills;
